{"arkId":"cl010092435","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010092435","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"T\u00eate de Christ couronn\u00e9 d\u0027\u00e9pines","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"T\u00eate de Christ couronn\u00e9 d\u0027\u00e9pines"},{"type":"Ancien titre","value":"Dieu de la Cit\u00e9"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1485 - 1500","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1485,"endYear":1500,"imprecision":"","text":"Fin du XVe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"France \u00cele-de-France","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RF 445","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"fragment de statue","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"0,235","displayDimension":"0,235 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"0,185","displayDimension":"0,185 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"0,175","displayDimension":"0,175 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"pierre traces de polychromie","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Origine incertaine. Magasins de Saint-Denis au XIXe si\u00e8cle. Versement des Chantiers de Saint-Denis, 1881 (arr\u00eat\u00e9 du 28 juillet 1881). Pourrait \u00eatre consid\u00e9r\u00e9 comme un fragment de la statue du Christ de Piti\u00e9 dit \u0022Dieu de la Cit\u00e9\u0022 qui figurait dans une niche du Vieux Charnier du cimeti\u00e8re des Innocents \u00e0 Paris. Cimeti\u00e8re ferm\u00e9 par arr\u00eat du 1er d\u00e9cembre 1780. Statue transport\u00e9e au lieu-dit la Tombe-Issoire o\u00f9 furent transf\u00e9r\u00e9s les vestiges et ossements du cimeti\u00e8re des Innocents. L\u0027oeuvre, signal\u00e9e en ce lieu le 25 juillet 1787, aurait \u00e9t\u00e9 remise \u00e0 cette date au chapitre de Notre-Dame. Pourrait avoir \u00e9t\u00e9 recueillie au mus\u00e9e des Monuments fran\u00e7ais et transmise \u00e0 Saint-Denis apr\u00e8s 1816. Date de mutilation inconnue. Le socle du \u0022Dieu de la Cit\u00e9\u0022 est peut-\u00eatre le RF 1235.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"versement","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"28\/07\/1881","startYear":1881,"endYear":1881}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"versement"}],"material":[{"value":"pierre"}],"technic":[{"value":"traces de polychromie"}],"objectType":[{"value":"fragment de statue"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Chancel-Bardelot, B\u00e9atrice de (dir.), Le mus\u00e9e des Monuments fran\u00e7ais d\u0027Alexandre Lenoir, histoire et collections, [INHA \/ Louvre], Paris, Institut National d\u0027Histoire de l\u0027Art, 2014, Disponible sur : \u0026lt;\thttps:\/\/agorha.inha.fr\/inhaprod\/ark:\/54721\/00145\u0026gt; ","bibliographyDate":"2014","bibliographyDetail":"https:\/\/agorha.inha.fr\/inhaprod\/ark:\/54721\/003135575","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Baron, Fran\u00e7oise, Mus\u00e9e du Louvre - Sculpture fran\u00e7aise - I - Moyen Age, Paris, 1996","bi